Global Dog DNA Test Service Market Insights
Dog DNA Test Service Market size was valued at USD 0.50 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.10 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Dog DNA Test Service Market Overview
The global dog DNA test service market is experiencing robust growth, with a market value expected to reach USD 1.5 billion by 2027, growing at a CAGR of 15.2%. This growth is attributed to rising pet ownership, increasing consumer interest in pet health and genetics, and advancements in DNA testing technology. Consumers are becoming more aware of the benefits of dog DNA testing, which provides insight into breed, health, and ancestry. These services are also being integrated into veterinary care, contributing to the market’s expansion. North America dominates the market, but the Asia-Pacific region is anticipated to show significant growth due to the rising pet population and increasing adoption rates.

